description:
The backend push-pr endpoint returns dict[str, str] but the frontend expects PushPRResponse.

## Backend (app/main.py line 107-114):
```python
@app.post("/api/projects/{project_id}/push-pr")
async def push_and_create_pr(
    project_id: str,
    request: PushPRRequest | None = None,
) -> dict[str, str]:  # Should be PushPRResponse
```

## Frontend expects (types.ts):
```typescript
export interface PushPRResponse {
  push: string;
  pr: string;
}
```

## Fix:
Change return type from dict[str, str] to PushPRResponse for type safety and API documentation.
